<h4> ALBEN MIPS<br />
PORA MIPS </h4>
<p>Unique solution that Mips has developed for our model ALBEN where the supreme Mips features are adapted to  our model, with the Mips layer under the pads system, and matching the pad shape, so to ensure  lightness, no extra sweating and fully compliance with the ventilation structure designed for the specific helmet model.</p>

